Piecable,Software,is,an,app,development,platform,It,allows,developers,retailers,companies,and,others,desiring,to,create,an,app,for,their,service,tools,to,construct,test,and,deploy,their,own,Pieceable,offers,a,simulator,platform,called,the,Pieceable,Viewer,to,upload,existing,apps,to,test,and,troubleshoot,them,Then,when,they,are,finished,they,can,be,published,directly,to,site,for,testing,or,demoing,The,Pieceable,API,exposes,the,Viewer,platform,and,allows,developers,to,integrate,uploading,with,their,scripts,It,is,a,RESTful,API,that,returns,JSON,encoded,data